---
import SectionHeader from '../ui/SectionHeader.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 lg:py-24 bg-brand-softBg">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <SectionHeader
      title="Why Work With TheEduAssist?"
    />

    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-brand-border/60 overflow-hidden">
        <ul class="divide-y divide-brand-border/40">
            <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">We combine disciplines.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We combine learning design, content structure, platform build, and launch support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">We bring order to chaos.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We help turn scattered content into learner-friendly systems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">Multi-platform expertise.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We understand Kajabi deeply, but we are not limited to Kajabi. We support LMS migration and various setups.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">End-to-end capabilities.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We support content conversion, AI-assisted production, funnels, and ongoing support.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
            <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">Dual focus.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We design for both your business goals and the learner's experience.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
             <li class="p-6 md:p-8 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors">
                <div class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-brand-accent mt-0.5 mr-4 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-primary mb-1">Systems over pages.</h3>
                        <p class="text-brand-textMain">We focus on launch-ready systems, not random pages or disconnected files.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
